# Walkthrough: Kaggle Profile Optimization

**Goal**: Elevate profile to "Expert" status by deploying high-quality notebooks for Spaceship Titanic and AIMO competitions.

## 🚀 Deployed Artifacts

### 1. Spaceship Titanic: Trinity Killshot [Expert]
- **URL**: [Spaceship Trinity Expert Final V1](https://www.kaggle.com/code/kiza123123/spaceship-trinity-expert-final-v1)
- **Status**: ✅ Version 1 Pushed
- **Key Features**:
    - **Trinity Protocol**: Thesis-Antithesis-Synthesis loop for model selection.
